---
title: "Noema — User Flow: File Operation + Index Sync"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Svelte Frontend
    participant Cmd as Command Router
    participant FOps as File Ops Engine
    participant FS as Filesystem
    participant EB as Event Bus
    participant Idx as Indexer
    participant DB as SQLite

    Note over User,DB: File Move via Explorer

    User->>UI: Drags file.pdf from /docs to /archive
    UI->>Cmd: move_files(["/docs/file.pdf"], "/archive/")
    Cmd->>FOps: move(sources, dest)

    FOps->>FOps: Push to undo stack
    FOps->>FS: std::fs::rename (same volume) or copy+delete
    FS-->>FOps: success
    FOps->>EB: FileChanged { path: "/archive/file.pdf", type: Moved }
    FOps-->>Cmd: OperationId
    Cmd-->>UI: Event::OperationComplete

    EB->>Idx: FileChanged event received
    Idx->>DB: UPDATE files SET path = '/archive/file.pdf' WHERE content_hash = 'abc...'

    Note right of DB: Annotations, tags, AI context,<br/>embeddings all preserved.<br/>Only path updated.

    DB-->>Idx: updated
    Idx->>EB: IndexUpdated { file_id }
    EB-->>UI: Refresh views

    Note over User,DB: Undo

    User->>UI: Cmd+Z (Undo)
    UI->>Cmd: undo()
    Cmd->>FOps: undo()
    FOps->>FOps: Pop undo stack → Move { from: /archive/file.pdf, to: /docs/file.pdf }
    FOps->>FS: rename back
    FS-->>FOps: success
    FOps->>EB: FileChanged { type: Moved }
    EB->>Idx: Update path back in DB

    Note over User,DB: External Change (detected by watcher)

    Note left of FS: User renames file via Terminal
    FS->>EB: notify event: Remove "/docs/old.pdf" + Create "/docs/new.pdf"
    EB->>Idx: Debounced (500ms)
    Idx->>DB: Lookup by content_hash
    Idx->>Idx: Hash match → same file, just renamed
    Idx->>DB: UPDATE path, filename
    Idx->>EB: IndexUpdated
    EB-->>UI: Refresh current view
